span.span: Thank you for your inquiry regarding the Community Facilities District ("CFD”) within the Val Verde Unified School District. The CFD has been an essential tool to help the School District build the necessary school facilities for our growing community. We hope you will be able to utilize this website as a resource for your questions regarding the Special Tax. If you have additional questions, please feel free to contact our Special Tax Administrator, Cooperative Strategies, LLC at 877.250.1503 or
